Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text: Frontage on Katy Mills Parkway with convenient access to Interstate-10 and the Grand Parkway

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE is pleased to present the opportunity to acquire 25403 Katy Mills Parkway (the Property), a 31,500 square foot property located in Katy, Texas. 
Built in 2008 as a state-of-the-art office training facility, the Property could provide an owner-user the opportunity to acquire highly efficient, quality accommodations with convenient access to Interstate 10 and the Grand Parkway (SH99). 

The Property is available for immediate occupancy in second generation space that is well positioned for an owner/user or corporate tenant seeking space on Houston’s west side, adjacent Katy Mills Shopping Center.
